### 订单服务 API 测试示例

### 1. 创建订单 - 面交
POST http://localhost:8083/orders?userId=1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "productName": "二手自行车",
  "productImage": "http://example.com/bike.jpg",
  "price": 299.00,
  "quantity": 1,
  "tradeType": "FACE_TO_FACE",
  "tradeLocation": "学校东门",
  "remark": "希望周末交易"
}

### 2. 创建订单 - 自提
POST http://localhost:8083/orders?userId=1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 2,
  "productName": "Java编程思想",
  "productImage": "http://example.com/book.jpg",
  "price": 59.90,
  "quantity": 1,
  "tradeType": "SELF_PICKUP",
  "tradeLocation": "图书馆门口",
  "remark": ""
}

### 3. 查询订单详情
GET http://localhost:8083/orders/1

### 4. 取消订单
POST http://localhost:8083/orders/cancel?userId=1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cancelReason": "不想买了"
}

### 5. 更新订单状态 - 待交付
PUT http://localhost:8083/orders/status?orderId=2&status=PENDING_DELIVERY&tradeLocation=图书馆门口

### 6. 更新订单状态 - 已完成
PUT http://localhost:8083/orders/status?orderId=2&status=COMPLETED

### 7. 查询我的订单 - 全部
GET http://localhost:8083/orders/my?userId=1001&pageNum=1&pageSize=10

### 8. 查询我的订单 - 待支付
GET http://localhost:8083/orders/my?userId=1001&status=PENDING_PAYMENT&pageNum=1&pageSize=10

### 9. 查询我的订单 - 已完成
GET http://localhost:8083/orders/my?userId=1001&status=COMPLETED&pageNum=1&pageSize=10

### 10. 订单列表查询 - 关键词搜索
GET http://localhost:8083/orders/list?keyword=自行车&pageNum=1&pageSize=10

### 11. 订单列表查询 - 按用户和状态
GET http://localhost:8083/orders/list?userId=1001&status=PENDING_PAYMENT&pageNum=1&pageSize=10
